README

Important points: 

- Building with g++ compiler:

$ g++ main.cpp Person.cpp Twitter.cpp Utility.cpp Resource.cpp -std=c++11 -o main
$ ./main

- Building with cmake (from the termimnal):

$ cmake . // to compile with current options and create the CMakeCahce.txt
$ ccmake . // to configure new options, i.e., new c and cpp compilers 
$ cmake .
$ make

